@startuml
title Widget Geometry and Viewport - Sequence View

skinparam ParticipantPadding 8

participant "FrameModule" as FrameModule
participant "Root Widget" as Root
participant "Parent Widget" as Parent
participant "Child Widget" as Child
participant "Viewport" as Viewport
participant "RenderSnapshotBuilder" as Builder

FrameModule -> Root : dispatch WindowResizedEvent
Root -> Root : update root geometry from frame
Root -> Parent : notify parent geometry changed
Parent -> Parent : recompute global rect
Parent -> Child : notify parent geometry changed
Child -> Child : recompute global rect

Root -> Viewport : create from frame rect
Root -> Builder : append viewport command
Parent -> Viewport : intersect parent rect
Parent -> Builder : append parent viewport
Child -> Viewport : intersect child rect with parent viewport
Child -> Builder : append child viewport

note bottom
Each child is clipped by its own geometry and by every
ancestor viewport before its drawing commands execute.
end note

@enduml
